WEBVTT

00:01:17.439 --> 00:01:17.959
Zheng Tao

00:01:35.280 --> 00:01:36.519
Zheng Tao, cover me.

00:02:07.079 --> 00:02:07.599
Xiao Jiu.

00:02:19.520 --> 00:02:20.120
Make the call.

00:02:21.520 --> 00:02:22.120
Make the call.

00:02:23.039 --> 00:02:23.759
Make the call.

00:02:25.080 --> 00:02:25.599
Don't move.

00:02:30.439 --> 00:02:31.199
Make the call.

00:02:32.599 --> 00:02:33.159
Don't move.

00:02:35.199 --> 00:02:36.000
Inspector Qi.

00:02:38.319 --> 00:02:40.719
Put the gun on the ground.

00:02:41.759 --> 00:02:42.479
Slide it over.

00:02:43.120 --> 00:02:44.560
Or I'll shoot her dead.

00:02:45.879 --> 00:02:46.439
Hurry up.

00:03:00.280 --> 00:03:01.039
Put it down slowly.

00:03:12.840 --> 00:03:13.439
Don't move.

00:03:21.120 --> 00:03:21.960
I found out...

00:03:22.240 --> 00:03:23.479
...there's a secret passage in the Tower of Babel.

00:03:23.960 --> 00:03:25.240
The money should be right there.

00:03:26.159 --> 00:03:26.719
Find it.

00:03:30.599 --> 00:03:32.919
Open the secret passage for me.

00:03:42.680 --> 00:03:43.719
Open the secret passage door.

00:03:45.080 --> 00:03:47.039
You need to turn two mechanisms in order.

00:03:49.560 --> 00:03:50.919
The first one is in the study upstairs.

00:03:51.919 --> 00:03:53.400
Cut the crap.

00:03:53.759 --> 00:03:54.840
Don't play tricks on me.

00:03:55.280 --> 00:03:56.560
Believe it or not, I'll kill you.

00:03:56.800 --> 00:03:57.840
What he says is true.

00:03:58.159 --> 00:03:59.400
There really are two mechanisms.

00:04:04.439 --> 00:04:05.159
You bitch.

00:04:06.199 --> 00:04:07.560
If you dare lie...

00:04:09.319 --> 00:04:10.800
...you'll end up like the one on the ground.

00:04:14.840 --> 00:04:15.400
You.

00:04:16.519 --> 00:04:17.639
Walk in front and lead the way.

00:04:18.240 --> 00:04:19.519
Go upstairs and open the mechanism.

00:04:21.560 --> 00:04:22.639
Hurry up.

00:04:24.600 --> 00:04:25.319
Move.

00:04:26.360 --> 00:04:26.879
Okay.

00:04:30.160 --> 00:04:30.720
I'll lead the way.

00:04:32.279 --> 00:04:33.040
Don't hurt her.

00:04:46.800 --> 00:04:47.800
Look forward.

00:04:52.240 --> 00:04:53.959
Don't look. Keep walking.

00:05:11.079 --> 00:05:12.000
Hands up.

00:05:19.959 --> 00:05:21.160
Zhao Qihai, calm down.

00:05:22.360 --> 00:05:23.079
Don't be rash.

00:05:25.800 --> 00:05:27.600
Even if you get Zhao Qishan's money, it's useless.

00:05:29.240 --> 00:05:30.720
The police already have evidence of your crimes.

00:05:32.720 --> 00:05:34.279
It's not too late to surrender now.

00:05:34.800 --> 00:05:35.720
You're not the ringleader.

00:05:36.839 --> 00:05:38.399
You can still strive for leniency.

00:05:39.319 --> 00:05:40.560
You still have many chances in life.

00:05:40.720 --> 00:05:42.519
Stop talking nonsense to me.

00:05:43.879 --> 00:05:45.000
Just tell me.

00:05:45.720 --> 00:05:46.720
Where is the mechanism?

00:05:54.000 --> 00:05:54.439
There.

00:05:55.120 --> 00:05:55.959
Where?

00:06:00.560 --> 00:06:01.120
The painting.

00:06:54.480 --> 00:06:55.079
Inspector Qi.

00:06:56.480 --> 00:06:57.000
Inspector Qi.

00:06:57.839 --> 00:06:58.399
Inspector Qi.

00:07:00.000 --> 00:07:00.519
Inspector Qi.

00:07:01.439 --> 00:07:02.000
Inspector Qi.

00:07:02.959 --> 00:07:03.480
Inspector Qi.

00:07:03.800 --> 00:07:04.399
Inspector Qi.

00:07:05.560 --> 00:07:06.120
Inspector Qi.

00:07:06.319 --> 00:07:07.199
Wake up, Inspector Qi.

00:07:08.040 --> 00:07:08.800
Inspector Qi.

00:07:09.360 --> 00:07:10.639
Inspector Qi, wake up.

00:07:10.839 --> 00:07:11.519
Inspector Qi.

00:07:13.120 --> 00:07:13.959
Wake up!

00:07:15.240 --> 00:07:15.839
Inspector Qi.

00:07:16.639 --> 00:07:17.199
Inspector Qi.

00:07:18.639 --> 00:07:19.240
Inspector Qi.

00:07:19.399 --> 00:07:20.079
Inspector Qi.

00:07:25.199 --> 00:07:26.879
Inspector Qi, don't give up.

00:07:27.879 --> 00:07:29.439
The puzzle is about to be solved.

00:07:30.879 --> 00:07:33.399
Only you can solve this case.

00:07:35.759 --> 00:07:36.399
Inspector Qi.

00:07:37.160 --> 00:07:39.360
There are so many victims in this case.

00:07:39.759 --> 00:07:41.879
Waiting for you to get them justice.

00:07:46.759 --> 00:07:48.120
I saw a ghost.

00:07:49.439 --> 00:07:50.399
There's a ghost.

00:07:53.399 --> 00:07:55.160
Brother Shan, I saw it just now.

00:07:56.639 --> 00:07:57.120
Brother Shan.

00:07:58.279 --> 00:07:59.519
I saw it just now.

00:08:00.399 --> 00:08:00.920
Brother Shan.

00:08:02.439 --> 00:08:04.160
She jumped down from here just now.

00:08:05.839 --> 00:08:06.879
She came to save us.

00:08:07.519 --> 00:08:08.199
This money...

00:08:09.040 --> 00:08:10.199
...you have to give me half.

00:08:13.120 --> 00:08:13.920
Don't give it to the Boss.

00:08:15.639 --> 00:08:17.160
Ghost!

00:08:18.879 --> 00:08:19.560
Brother Shan.

00:08:20.879 --> 00:08:21.839
Save me!

00:08:22.040 --> 00:08:22.839
Brother Shan.

00:08:23.360 --> 00:08:24.240
She burned herself.

00:08:24.639 --> 00:08:25.480
The money is mine.

00:08:26.279 --> 00:08:26.759
Brother Shan.

00:08:27.560 --> 00:08:28.600
Brother Shan, come here.

00:08:29.720 --> 00:08:30.199
Brother Shan.

00:09:17.240 --> 00:09:17.840
Inspector Qi

00:09:18.360 --> 00:09:19.279
Li Ran and Li Ren

00:09:19.440 --> 00:09:20.799
have been in touch for years.

00:09:20.960 --> 00:09:21.919
Call for backup immediately.

00:09:22.600 --> 00:09:23.519
Come to the Tower of Babel.

00:09:25.279 --> 00:09:25.759
Li Ran.

00:09:51.159 --> 00:09:53.080
I was just too scared just now.

00:09:54.080 --> 00:09:55.600
I just wanted to hurry back here to hide.

00:09:58.000 --> 00:09:59.440
How did you open this coded door?

00:09:59.960 --> 00:10:01.440
Didn't you tell me you didn't know?